## Configuracion

### Global — `config/global_settings.py`

Aplica a todos los jobs. Modificar solo en casos excepcionales (cambio de encoding, separador CSV, etc.).

```python
LOG_CONFIG  = {"log_folder": "log", "level": "INFO"}
DATA_CONFIG = {
    "csv":  {"encoding": "utf-8", "separator": ";", "index": False},
    "json": {"indent": 2, "force_ascii": False, "orient": "records"},
    "xml":  {"root": "registros", "row": "registro", "encoding": "utf-8"},
    "xlsx": {"sheet_name": "Datos", "index": False}
}
```

### Por job — `src/<job>/settings.py`

```python
DRIVER_CONFIG = {
    "headless":    False,   # True: sin ventana (produccion/servidores)
    "undetected":  True,    # True: evasion anti-bot (Cloudflare, reCAPTCHA)
    "maximize":    True,
    "window_size": None,    # Ej: (1920, 1080)
    "user_agent":  None,    # Ej: "Mozilla/5.0 ..."
    "proxy":       None     # Ej: "192.168.1.1:8080"
}

STORAGE_CONFIG = {
    "output_folder":  "output/<job>",
    "filename":       "<job>",
    "naming_mode":    "date_suffix",   # overwrite | date_suffix | timestamp_suffix | date_folder
    "output_formats": ["csv", "json"]  # csv | json | xml | xlsx
}

RAW_CONFIG = {
    "raw_folder": "raw/<job>",
    "filename":   "<job>",
    "format":     "csv",
    "retention":  {"mode": "keep_last_n", "value": 5}
    # retention modes: keep_all | keep_last_n | keep_days
}

SKIP_PROCESS = False  # True: omite process.py, guarda raw como output
```

#### Modos de nombrado (`naming_mode`)

| Modo | Archivo generado |
|---|---|
| `overwrite` | `output/<job>/<job>.csv` — sobreescribe siempre |
| `date_suffix` | `output/<job>/<job>_20260130.csv` — uno por dia |
| `timestamp_suffix` | `output/<job>/<job>_20260130_143052.csv` — uno por ejecucion |
| `date_folder` | `output/<job>/20260130/<job>.csv` — organizado por fecha |

